"multiple compilers associated with it, and this function only returns one of "
"them. It can be better to refer to compilers on a per-language basis, "
"through the language virtuals: ``spec[\"c\"]``, ``spec[\"cxx\"]``, and "
"``spec[\"fortran\"]``."
msgstr ""

